    {
        "content": "<p>I note that various stronger forms exist (see e.g., this <a href=\"https://mathoverflow.net/questions/26/can-a-vector-space-over-an-infinite-field-be-a-finite-union-of-proper-subspaces\">MO question</a> or this <a href=\"https://mathoverflow.net/questions/295214/modules-over-infinite-rings-which-can-not-be-a-finite-union-of-their-proper-subm\">MO question</a> but IMHO this statement would be worth a PR in its own right.</p>",
